1. Na *polju* ima mnogo kukuruza. (In the *field* there is a lot of corn.)
2. Danas sam išao na *polje* da berem jagode. (Today I went to the *field* to pick strawberries.)
3. Njiva na *polju* nije obrađena već dugo vremena. (The field on the *field* hasn't been cultivated for a long time.)
4. Žetva na *polju* počinje za nekoliko dana. (The harvest in the *field* begins in a few days.)
5. Prošle godine smo imali dobru berbu na *polju*. (Last year we had a good harvest in the *field*.)
6. Ovaj deo *polja* je posebno plodan. (This part of the *field* is particularly fertile.)
7. Vozio sam traktor po *poljima* celog dana. (I drove a tractor through the *fields* all day.)
8. Ove godine su usevi na *poljima* bolji nego prošle godine. (This year the crops in the *fields* are better than last year.)
9. Stoka je pasla na *polju* pored puta. (The cattle were grazing on the *field* next to the road.)
10. Ljubitelji prirode često odlaze u šetnju po *poljima*. (Nature lovers often go for a walk through the *fields*.)